{"tid":1366256,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"追究黑警!!!!!","createTime":"2019-07-26T01:53:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T02:03:22.000Z","uid":8044,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fba46e6a4e785fe1e6a7e35b9895a5a6f6950646","tid":1366256,"uid":8044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:53:36.000Z","msg":"Sorry 被我個標題呃咗你入嚟<br />\n但係我成日都聽到啲深藍喺度講<br />\n你咁叻 要求譴責黑警 <br />\n有事上嚟唔好報謷<br />\n我同你班藍絲講<br />\n我同你一樣 絕對支持警察執法<br />\n但係唔係支持 唔遵從《警察通例》係冇警示下用催淚彈<br />\n甚至係使用布袋彈、橡膠子彈、海綿彈去打落示威者頭部<br />\n我明白 示威者有時可能行動激進<br />\n但係 諗深一層 當一位警察唔再遵從《警察通例》你同一個有槍嘅暴徒有咩分別 因此必須追究違返《警察通例》而且濫用其權力嘅警察<br />\n仲有好多事件以包括元朗警黑勾結以令香港人對警察執法失去信心 甚至係警方自己都軍心渙散 <br />\n試問有邊個國家嘅警民關係咁樣<br />\n因此必須成立獨立調查委員會 徹查於近日示威濫權嘅警察<br />\n廉政公署亦必須向市民交代元朗警黑勾結事件<br />\n藉此重拾市民對警隊嘅信心以及執法嘅信任<br />\n<br />\nBy一個見到警察正常執法嘅和平理非<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力"},{"pid":"b05e64ec710eef62af5ba2850ca805b09b5cdfa0","tid":1366256,"uid":127858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">兄弟爬山</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">各有各做</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化不篤灰不割席</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fb18fc7321a976c0fbe70d8040cc9730aa5301","tid":1366256,"uid":286990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"追究黑警濫權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />